                     <a class="story-type" href="/americanlawyer/news/">News</a>

        
                <h1 itemprop="name">In a Hot Lateral Market, Why Are Some Lawyers Lifers?</h1>
                <h4 class="article-description hidden-xs hidden-sm">More attorneys than ever are ready to change firms, but loyalty and satisfaction keep some eyes from wandering.</h4>


<!-- this has a domainId: 12 -->

<!--
plc-tal
-->




<div class="social-byline">
<div class="byline">




                    
                    
                        <span class="top-info" itemprop="author">By 

                          <a href="/author/profile/Dylan-Jackson/"><strong>Dylan Jackson</strong></a>

                
        </span>




    <span class="pipe">|</span>
    <span class="top-info">April 02, 2019 at 03:57 PM</span>





    
					        
</div>

<div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>
        </div>
        </div>


        
<div id="article-standard" class="row">
    <div id="article-left-col" class="col-lg-8">
        <div class="row">
