    <input type="hidden" name="theHeadline" id="theHeadline" value="In a Hot Lateral Market, Why Are Some Lawyers Lifers?">
    <input type="hidden" name="theDescription" id="theDescription" value="More attorneys than ever are ready to change firms, but loyalty and satisfaction keep some eyes from wandering.">
    <input type="hidden" name="theLink" id="theLink" value="https://www.law.com/americanlawyer/2019/04/02/law-firm-lifers-and-the-hot-lateral-market-405-34451/?cmp=share_email">
    <button type="submit" class="send-article">Send</button>
    <div id="sendnow">sending now...</div>
