                     <a class="story-type" href="/corpcounsel/best-practices/">Best Practices</a>

        
                <h1 itemprop="name">The Legal Risks of Targeted Ads: Lawyers Weigh In on Avoiding Anti-Discrimination Violations</h1>
                <h4 class="article-description hidden-xs hidden-sm">A new suit against Facebook alleges the platform allowed advertisers to engage in housing discrimination. For platforms offering targeted ads, the suit is a warning to check advertiser policies and ad review processes. </h4>


<!-- this has a domainId: 15 -->

