                <p class="author">

                        
                        <!-- no author url -->
                                                <a href="/author/profile/Dan-Clark/">Dan Clark</a>    
                         
 |
                <time>April 01, 2019</time>
                </p>
                <p>In a new survey, 49 percent of information technology leaders say employees have accidentally put sensitive data at risk between one to 10 times in the past year while 61 percent believe employees put out this data maliciously.</p>  
