        <div class="article-info container">

                     <a class="story-type" href="/corpcounsel/news/">News</a>

        
                <h1 itemprop="name">Report: Disconnection Between Security Officials and Employees on Data Breaches</h1>
                <h4 class="article-description">In a new survey, 49 percent of information technology leaders say employees have accidentally put sensitive data at risk between one to 10 times in the past year while 61 percent believe employees put out this data maliciously.</h4>


<!-- this has a domainId: 15 -->

<!--
plc-cc
-->




